Ashley Roberts changed into a see-through blue dress for the post-awards celebrations. Alex Scott appeared in high spirits as she was snapped on the car journey home from the awards show after-party. Similarly, despite a late night at the BRITs, Leigh-Anne appeared as flawless as usual as she made her way to an afterparty in her fiery orange dress. Meanwhile, Billie Piper upped the ante as she slipped into a barely-there ensemble for the Warner Music and Ciroc Brit Awards Party at The Nomad Hotel on Saturday. The actress, 40, joined the music industry's elite at the star-studded bash, following an action-packed awards ceremony held at London's O2 Arena.